79.storedString:
What to do:

- Press "Open FRP Inspector" button.
- Press the "+" button in the FRP Inspector.
- Type in "timer".
- Select "timer" in the list.
- In the top-right pane, type in:
    durationE(20, 20000)
- Hit Cmd-s to accept the change.
- Select "--ALL--" to see the values.

262.source:
function instanciateStreams() {
    var list = [["heading1", "0 fby heading1' + speed1 on timer"],
     ["heading2", "0 fby heading2' + speed2 on timer"],
     ["heading3", "0 fby heading3' + speed3 on timer"],
     ["heading4", "0 fby heading4' + speed4 on timer"],
     ["heading5", "0 fby heading5' + speed5 on timer"],
     ["heading6", "0 fby heading6' + speed6 on timer"],
     ["length1", "120"],
     ["length2", "length1 / 2"],
     ["length3", "length1 / 3"],
     ["length4", "length1 / 4"],
     ["length5", "length1 / 5"],
     ["length6", "length1 / 6"],
     ["speed1", "0.03"],
     ["speed2", "-0.09"],
     ["speed3", "0.15"],
     ["speed4", "-0.21"],
     ["speed5", "0.27"],
     ["speed6", "-0.33"]];

    list.forEach(function(pair) {
        lively.bindings.FRPCore.EventStream.fromString(pair[1])
            .installTo(this, pair[0])
    }.bind(this.get("FRPTest")));
}
